  <brief_title>Evaluation of Desloratadine When Used in Patients With Either Allergic Rhinitis or Chronic Idiopathic Urticaria</brief_title>
  <acronym>Aerius</acronym>
  <official_title>Post-marketing Surveillance of the Safety, Tolerability and Efficacy of Desloratadine Tablet Among Filipino Patients</official_title>
