  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Eligible patients will be prescribed Desloratadine 1 tablet of 5 mg once daily. Patients will
      be asked to follow-up for a final visit after 14 days (Day 15) where the safety, tolerability
      and clinical efficacy will be measured.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
