    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Outpatient men or women, age 12 years and above.

          -  Diagnosis of Allergic Rhinitis or Chronic Idiopathic Urticaria

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Known hypersensitivity to Desloratadine.

          -  Pregnancy or lactation
      </textblock>
